01:23:14.200 --> 01:23:15.000 align:middle line:90%
It's consciousness.

01:23:15.000 --> 01:23:17.050 align:middle line:90%
>> It's super consciousness.

01:23:17.050 --> 01:23:22.830 align:middle line:84%
And she hangs around the brain,
not the sole of your foot.

01:23:22.830 --> 01:23:26.240 align:middle line:84%
She's going to hang
around the brain.

01:23:26.240 --> 01:23:28.910 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, Ramana Maharshi
says it's right here.

01:23:28.910 --> 01:23:29.710 align:middle line:90%
>> In the heart.

01:23:29.710 --> 01:23:30.440 align:middle line:90%
Oh, the heart.

01:23:30.440 --> 01:23:31.310 align:middle line:90%
>> In the heart.

01:23:31.310 --> 01:23:35.300 align:middle line:84%
>> I've had to tell 1,000
