01:27:13.520 --> 01:27:15.520 align:middle line:84%
He was surrounded by
friends to the end.

01:27:15.520 --> 01:27:19.300 align:middle line:90%


01:27:19.300 --> 01:27:23.830 align:middle line:10%
>> Sometime in the last seven
hours of his life, he said,

01:27:23.830 --> 01:27:25.390 align:middle line:10%
compadre.

01:27:25.390 --> 01:27:28.420 align:middle line:10%
And then he said,
