01:27:42.310 --> 01:27:43.460 align:middle line:90%
Why?

01:27:43.460 --> 01:27:45.160 align:middle line:90%
Why?

01:27:45.160 --> 01:27:48.970 align:middle line:84%
Followed by an almost
mantra-like repetition

01:27:48.970 --> 01:27:50.695 align:middle line:84%
of the words "why
not," "why not."

01:27:50.695 --> 01:27:58.620 align:middle line:90%


01:27:58.620 --> 01:28:01.230 align:middle line:10%
>> Here in Southern California
, the Harvard professor who

01:28:01.230 --> 01:28:05.610 align:middle line:10%
became the outlaw acid
king of the 1960s is dead.

