Dr. Timothy Leary advocated
the use of mind-bending drugs.

01:28:09.220 --> 01:28:10.020 align:middle line:10%
In recent years--

01:28:10.020 --> 01:28:14.590 align:middle line:10%
>> And there were 25 or 26
messages from CBS, and CNN,

01:28:14.590 --> 01:28:16.470 align:middle line:10%
on ABC, and da da da da da da.

01:28:16.470 --> 01:28:19.860 align:middle line:84%
And so I called "The Washington
Post," and I said, yes?

01:28:19.860 --> 01:28:24.540 align:middle line:84%
How do you feel about your
