01:28:36.660 --> 01:28:39.760 align:middle line:90%
wasn't playing by the script.

01:28:39.760 --> 01:28:44.700 align:middle line:84%
He and I have met in
ideas and experiences

01:28:44.700 --> 01:28:49.350 align:middle line:84%
